@startuml
title Отправка уведомления и фиксация аудита

actor Operator as "Сотрудник деканата"
participant "NotificationService" as Service
participant "Configuration" as Config
participant "NotificationProvider" as Provider
participant "NotificationAuditor" as Auditor

Operator -> Service: send(request)
Service -> Config: notificationProviderType(), auditEnabled()
Config --> Service: channel="email", audit=true
Service -> Provider: send(channel, recipient, text)
Provider --> Service: success
alt аудит включён
  Service -> Auditor: record(sender, recipient, appealId, channel, result)
end
Service --> Operator: NotificationResult

note right of Config
Singleton-вариант получает Config глобально.
DI-вариант получает Config через конструктор.
end note
@enduml
